00:00:47.117 --> 00:00:49.130
Eric Schmidt:
that the norm must change.

00:00:49.130 --> 00:00:51.404 position:81%
Eric Schmidt:
What we want to do is we want to constantly reinvent

00:00:51.404 --> 00:00:52.920 position:58%
Eric Schmidt:
ourselves. Now it's easy to say that.

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:55.209 position:73%
Eric Schmidt:
How do you do it? In our case, we encourage our

00:00:55.209 --> 00:00:58.727 position:98%
Eric Schmidt:
employees to spend 20 percent of their time working on whatever

00:00:58.727 --> 00:01:01.960 position:84%
Eric Schmidt:
