00:01:11.468 --> 00:01:13.430 position:59%
Eric Schmidt:
Many different leadership styles work.

00:01:13.430 --> 00:01:17.825 position:89%
Eric Schmidt:
There's not one leadership style that is the way in which

00:01:17.825 --> 00:01:20.730
Eric Schmidt:
corporations, institutions succeed.

00:01:20.730 --> 00:01:24.159 position:95%
Eric Schmidt:
You'll have passionate, charismatic and disorganized leaders.

00:01:24.159 --> 00:01:27.459 position:81%
Eric Schmidt:
